1. How to build it?
    Just run make.
2. How to play with it?
    server(beta):
    (1) run tcpd as daemon. 
        tcpd -s & 
    (2) run ftps.
        ftps 1115
    client: 
    (1) ssh to new host, and run troll
        troll 7000 -x0
    (2) open a new terminal. run tcpd as daemon
        tcpd -c &
    (3) run ftpc
        ftpc beta 1115 <local-file-to-transfer>

   if everything goes well, the file will be saved in "recv" folder on server.
